                <note type="updated" update="title" import="tengyur-data-3400-3485_PH_new_v2.4.xml" date-time="2021-11-02T14:07:38.426Z" user="admin">The title reflects a passage early in the text which states “having recited [this mantra] one hundred and eight times, and having applied powdered bean paste
